description: Maximum of maximum monthly GW used as water supply source at Sutter NWR assuming "New Level 2 and Level 4" delivery schedule and historical surface water deliveries from SEWD and Sutter Bypass. Source: E-mail correspondence with Rachel Esralew, Hydrologist, USFWS regarding the Sutter NWR delivery alternatives explored in the Sutter NWR Water Supply Report published Nov 2014. - Karandev Singh 6.4.2017
